fields.name: PONumber
fields.description: PO Number resulted after the PO Matching step (or PO Number to use if the Matching is skipped)

fields.name: ExtractedPONumber
fields.description: PO Number extracted by the DU Process

fields.name: InternalFASystemID
fields.description: The ID of the Invoice once added in the internal F&A application (e.g. Coupa)

fields.name: Source
fields.description: Should represent the source where the invoice was retrieved from. By Default this can be  Email, SharedDrive but more values can be added in the Source ChoiceSet.

fields.name: Quantity
fields.description: This field should be used in relation with the UnitPrice Field

fields.name: TotalAmount
fields.description: Can either represent the Amount of a non quantity Line Item OR the total between Unit Amount * Quanitity

fields.name: LinePONumber
fields.description: Number of the corresponding PO Line

fields.name: UnitPrice
fields.description: This field should be used in relation with the Quantity Field

fields.name: Invoice
fields.description: The Parent Invoice this line item belongs to
